# testcase
# step 1.
I switch consoles to 1024x768(75Hz,32bpp) mode.
http://149.156.124.14/~pluto/tmp/kernel/step1.png
# step 2.
I launch a bootsplash and see that consoles switches
to a strange resolution and horrible aspect ratio.
http://149.156.124.14/~pluto/tmp/kernel/step2.png
Even without launching a bootsplash while switching
to another console I observe above effect.
# step 3.
I switch consoles again to 1024x768(75Hz,32bpp) mode
and get an oops.
http://149.156.124.14/~pluto/tmp/kernel/step3.png
I've tested it on bootsplash-3.1.4-sp3 ported to 2.6.8rc2.
Do You have any ideas?
